en_153481_0	A man who assaulted his wife has committed suicide by hanging in Dikyaya area, Buttala.
en_153481_1	His wife was hospitalized with injuries after he assaulted her last morning, police said.
en_153481_2	She was transferred from the area hospital to Sirigala due to health complications.
en_153481_3	Following her statement the police has gone to her house in a bid to arrest the suspect, but has found him dead, Buttala police said.
